ows]], [[Linux]], [[OS X]], [[iOS]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/02/12/fahrenheit-indigo-prophecy-remastered-review |title=Fahrenheit: Indigo Prophecy Remastered Review |last=Rudden |first=Dave |date=12 February 2015 |website=IGN |access-date=23 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Fantasy Zone]]''\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[arcade game|Arcade]]\n|''[[Sega Ages#Sega Ages 2500|Sega Ages 2500]] Vol. 3: Fantasy Zone'' {{Vgrelease/region|JP}} || [[PlayStation 2]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/ps2/915127-sega-ages-2500-series-vol-3-fantasy-zone |title=Sega Ages 2500 Series Vol. 3: Fantasy Zone for PlayStation 2 |website=GameFAQs |language=en |access-date=23 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Sega Classics Collection]] Vol. 3'' {{Vgrelease/region|NA}} {{Vgrelease/region|EU}} || [[PlayStation 2]]\n|<ref name=\"sega_classic_collection\" >{{Cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/sega-classics-collection-review/1900-6121476/ |title=Sega Classics Collection Review |last=Gerstmann |first=Jeff |date=1 April 2005 |website=GameSpot |access-date=23 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Fatal Frame II: Crimson Butterfly]]'' ||rowspan=\"2\"| PlayStation 2\n| ''Fatal Frame II: Crimson Butterfly \u2013 Director's Cut''\n| Xbox\n|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Goldstein |first1=Hilary |title=Fatal Frame II: Crimson Butterfly - Director's Cut |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/10/19/fatal-frame-ii-crimson-butterfly-directors-cut |website=IGN |accessdate=15 October 2016 |date=18 October 2004 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925235545/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/10/19/fatal-frame-ii-crimson-butterfly-directors-cut |archivedate=25 September 2015 }}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Project Zero 2: Wii Edition]]'' || Nintendo Wii\n|<ref>{{cite web|last=Dunham |first=Jeremy |title=Fatal Frame II: Crimson Butterfly Review |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2003/11/19/fatal-frame-ii-crimson-butterfly |work=[[IGN]] |accessdate=1